I've searched for 'Maya Tunic' and clicked the search button. Now I can see the search results showing multiple entries related to 'Maya Tunic'. Looking at the table, I can see the main configurable product 'Maya Tunic' with ID 1780 in the first row, along with its various size and color variants (like Maya Tunic-S-Green, Maya Tunic-M-White, etc.) in the subsequent rows.

Since my goal is to edit the details of the 'Maya Tunic' product, I need to click on the 'Edit Maya Tunic' link in the Action column of the first row. This link has the BID 2250 and will take me to the product edit page where I can modify the product details.
